'''OIC'''

' 'Ururka Iskaashiga Islaamka' '' '' '' 'OIC' ''; {{lang-ar | منظمة التعاون الإسلامي | Munaẓẓama at-Taʿāwun al-ʾIslāmiyy}}; {{lang-fr | Ururka de la iskaashiga islamique}}), oo hore u ahaa '' '' Ururka Shirka Islaamka '' '', waa urur caalami ah oo la aasaasay 1969, kana kooban [[Dawladaha Xubinta ka ah Ururka Iskaashiga Islaamka | 57 dal ee xubnaha ka ah]], oo ay ku nool yihiin dad wada jira oo ka badan 1.8 bilyan illaa 2015 oo 49 dal ay yihiin dalal Muslimiin u badan. <ref> [[Pew Forum | Madasha Pew ee Diinta iyo Nolosha Dadweynaha]]. Diisambar 2012. "[https://assets.pewresearch.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/11/2014/01/global-religion-full.pdf The Global Religious Landscape: Report on the Size and Distribution of the Kooxaha Diinta ee ugu waaweyn Adduunka laga bilaabo 2010]. " DC: Xarunta Cilmi -baarista Pew. [https://www.pewforum.org/2012/12/18/global-religious-landscape-exec/ Article]. </ref> Ururku wuxuu sheegayaa inay tahay "codka wadajirka ah ee [[dunida Muslimka]] "wuxuuna ka shaqeeyaa" dhawridda iyo ilaalinta danaha dunida muslimka iyadoo laga duulayo dhiirrigelinta [[nabadda caalamiga ah]] iyo wada noolaanshaha ". <ref name =" EIMW "> [https://web.archive.org/web/ 20131030064136/http: //www.oic-oci.org/oicv2/page/? P_id = 52 & p_ref = 26 & lan = en Ku saabsan OIC]. Oic-oci.org. La soo ceshaday 7 Noofambar 2014. </ref>
25kii Sebtember 1969kii, Shir Islaami ah, oo ay ka qaybgaleen wakiilo ka kala socday 24 dal oo Muslimiin u badan (inta badan wakiiladu waxay ahaayeen madax dawladeed), ayaa lagu qabtay [[Rabat]], Morocco. <Ref name = "ECSWWII" /> < ref name = "EIMW" /> Waxaa la soo saaray qaraar sheegaya in <blockquote> "Dowladda Muslimka ah ay la tashan doonto si kor loogu qaado iskaashiga dhow iyo is kaashiga dhinacyada dhaqaalaha, sayniska, dhaqanka iyo ruuxa, oo ay dhiirrigelisay waxbarista aan dhiman ee Islaamka. "<ref name =" ECSWWII " /> </blockquote> Lix bilood ka dib bishii Maarj 1970kii, shirkii ugu horreeyey ee Wasiirrada Arrimaha Dibadda ee Islaamka ayaa lagu qabtay [[Jiddah]], Sacuudi Carabiya. <ref name =" elibrary " /> 1972kii ayaa la aasaasay Ururka Shirka Islaamka (OIC, oo hadda ah Ururka Iskaashiga Islaamka). <Ref name = "esposito-1998-164"> Esposito, 1998, p.164. </ref>

In kasta oo [[Masaajidka Al-Aqsa | al-Aqsa]] dabka loo arko mid ka mid ah waxyaabaha kiciyay aasaaskii OIC, qaar badan [[Muslimiin]] ayaa ku taamayey in ay yeeshaan hay’ad Islaami ah oo u adeegi doonta siyaasadda guud, danaha dhaqaale, iyo bulsho ee '' [[ummah]] '' (bulshada Muslimiinta) ilaa qarnigii 19aad. Gaar ahaan, burburkii [[Boqortooyadii Cusmaaniyiinta]] iyo [[Khilaafadii]] kadib [[Dagaalkii Koowaad ee Adduunka]] ka dib waxay ka tagtay meel bannaan.

Sida ku cad axdigiisa, Ururka Iskaashiga Islaamka wuxuu hiigsanayaa inuu ilaaliyo qiyamka bulshada iyo dhaqaalaha Islaamka; kor u qaadida wadajirka ka dhexeeya dawladaha xubnaha ka ah; kordhinta iskaashiga dhinacyada bulshada, dhaqaalaha, dhaqanka, sayniska, iyo siyaasadda; in la ilaaliyo nabadda iyo amniga caalamiga ah; iyo horumarinta waxbarashada, gaar ahaan dhinacyada sayniska iyo farsamada. <ref name = "EIMW" />

Astaanta OIC waxaa ku jira saddex arrimood oo waaweyn oo ka tarjumaya aragtidiisa iyo himiladiisa sida lagu daray Axdiga cusub. Curiyeyaashaasi waa: [[Kacbada]], Globe, iyo Bisha Cas.
